Postgraduate Program In Business Intelligence And Analytics For Hospitality Tourism postgraduate Who is it for?
This Postgraduate is aimed at senior managers, public and private technicians, consultants, entrepreneurs, and other professionals who wish to acquire analytical skills in data science in the field of tourism, using the most advanced information management technologies, data collection and analysis methodologies. Goals The goal of this is to train technical staff and managers to: Acquire Business Intelligence and Business Analytics competences applied to the hospitality and tourism sector; Deepen analytical and problem-solving skills within a highly dynamic and competitive industry; Update management and marketing knowledge in the context of digital transformation in a big data era that poses constant challenges to tourism organizations and companies; Develop hospitality and tourism analytics projects integrating concepts and tools worked throughout the .
